title: [FSX/P3D] LYBE V2, LDOS X, LYTV X
description:
Tested and works in FSX, FSX:SE, P3D v1, V2, V3 and V4. For any error please submit a comment on this thread.

The reason why I decided to upload this scenery file is because the website on which they were has been taken down (they were freeware). 

Would like to pass my gratitude to Djordje Kosanović for his work and his commitment to flightsim community. May you live long and prosper!

And fellas, 
Dare2Seed!
